room_title: Escape room "Crime Scene" by Escape 60 Peoria in Peoria
room_address: 931 N Sheridan Rd Suite B Peoria, IL 61606
room_description:
The infamous Prophecy killer has struck again, the 6th body was found this morning in a warehouse. As a reporter for the Journal Star, you began receiving notes from the serial killer soon after you first used the name Prophecy in an article after the 2nd murder.
You have just received another note from the killer threatening another murder in one hour. Desperate to find the killer before he claims another victim you have snuck into the warehouse to look for clues the cops may have missed during the forensic investigation earlier today. The door has locked behind you! Time is ticking to find the killers identity and get out. A life is in your hands and it may be yours!
